title: Eyelashes
content: The eyelashes are the windows of the eyes of the face.  How Poetic!

title: Bang!
content: I'm in the simulator, I'm doin' a-okay.  But every day is just rewind and replay.  Not today (ah).  I'll head out to Monterey.  Throw my phone into the waves.  Can you see it in my eyes? Am I finally awake?

title: So I cut you off!
content: I cut you off.  i dont need ya love.  so you can try all you want.  your time is up ill tell you why.  you say sorry but its too late now.
